{"tid":1658744,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"香港民研指六成半受訪市民不滿施政報告","createTime":"2019-10-16T15:04:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T15:09:18.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"55aee124c31acbd63401d32d8e208543ca64bb8c","tid":1658744,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:04:32.000Z","msg":"香港民意研究計劃在特首林鄭月娥發表施政報告後進行民調，受訪者對施政報告的平均評分為29.7，17%的受訪者表示滿意， 65%感到不滿，滿意淨值為 -48%，全部數據為歷來新低。<br />\n<br />\n民調以電腦隨機抽樣電話訪問及預先隨機抽樣的「追蹤」樣本形式進行，於下午約1時開始至晚上約8時結束，錄得745個成功個案，有679人表示有聽過施政報告。"},{"pid":"260a699e243dde5049345c18f06ebec58b9a070a","tid":1658744,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:05:11.000Z","msg":"滿意至奇啦<br />\n深紅就乜都滿意"},{"pid":"4d8acd2b551403bf20da109a0e94b7db69f8a895","tid":1658744,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:09:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwJzHzo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwJzHzo.jpg&h=eb217258&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"}]}